    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年4月14日-2025年4月18日）",
    "followRuleId": "1229254287192887296",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; padding: 0px; border: 1px none windowtext;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; padding: 0px; border: 1px none windowtext;\">本周共公示5条规则，生效9条规则，新增1篇规则解读。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; padding: 0px; border: 1px none windowtext;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 32px; line-height: 64px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227853250259193856&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台五金/</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">工具类目销售激励政策（2025.04.01-2025.06.30</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：在激励周期内，若店铺入驻时间&gt;3个月且店铺在五金/工具类目下有效销售额达到标准，将给予相应奖励，激励金于次月出具返利单完成并审批后返还至商家京准通账户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226803954231414784&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台办公设备类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：在激励周期内，在激励周期内成功启用店铺且经营时长不小于2个月的商家，<span style=\"color: black;\">若自然月对应类目有效销售额达目标门槛，将返还对应类目运营支持服务费率至京东钱包。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226351795111071744&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台运动户外类目资质标准》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：取消阿迪耐克品牌的邀约入驻限制，调整其余的品牌的入驻授权层级要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1229386673343827968\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台LOC</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商品管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：①调整LOC服务范围；②调整LOC商品及订单管理规范；③新增LOC商品订单结算规则；④新增LOC码无法使用的场景和规则；⑤修订未核销退款纠纷规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1229271919015104512&amp;btype=7\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台医药商家违规异地发货管理规范》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：调整违规处置措施及违约金额。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 32px; line-height: 64px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; padding: 0px; border: 1px none windowtext;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226706265988796416\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台机电散热类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在2025年6月30日前首次成功启用且经营时间不小于30天的店铺，返还对应类目下有效销售总额的一定百分比运营支持服务费至商家钱包。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226805716044615680\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台汽车用品类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新商家在规则周期内入驻且经营（或主营）以上品类商品享受质保金优惠政策，质保金调整至1000元，无需补交；除部分特殊类目外，新商家入驻前3个自然月，费率降至1%，3个月后维持标准费率不变。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226803954231414784\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台办公设备类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在激励周期内成功启用店铺且经营时长不小于2个月的商家，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;\">若自然月对应类目有效销售额达目标门槛，将返还对应类目运营支持服务费率至京东钱包。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227853250259193856\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台五金/</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">工具类目销售激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在激励周期内，若店铺入驻时间&gt;3个月且店铺在五金/工具类目下有效销售额达到标准，平台将给予相应奖励，激励金返还至商家京准通账户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227797943176794112\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台招商管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整同品牌在京东招商开放平台的开店数量。品牌可以根据自身发展需要，在不同的类目下开设旗舰店，同时基于经营表现或用户体验，京东对品牌开设旗舰店的数量会进行动态评估。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226731001624006656\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台发货管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b;\">调整关于虚拟业务、少错件、晚发赔的管理范围及标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090224406216708096&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">个体交易管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227811979650011136\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台质保期服务规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①增加质保维修争议场景说明和处理标准：涉及无故拒绝维修场景、超时未维修/维修超时未寄回、维修费用争议、多次维修未解决、维修后争议等场景；②调整平台类目最低质保期时效。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/noticeDetail.action?id=1227874570917253120\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年五一劳动节期间延迟结算公告》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">根据清算机构关于节假日期间跨行资金清算的安排，2025年4月30日至5月5日期间的交易将在2025年5月6日统一结算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 32px; line-height: 64px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 32px;\"><img src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/popXue/jfs/t1/284555/9/22532/48646/6801f956F06e16210/93ec8cb9a9b75980.dpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 100px 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 32px; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">1、<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1230412782491537408&amp;btype=15\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 38px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新品规则常见问题解答</span></a></span></p>",
    "selectCategoryId": [
      "1208614779573374976",
